#: ../../source/api/use_qteasy.rst:2
msgid "启动QTEASY"
msgstr "Start QTEASY"

#: ../../source/api/use_qteasy.rst:4
msgid "启动qteasy的配置信息:"
msgstr "Manage `qteasy` start up configurations"

#: of qteasy.core.run:1
msgid "根据当前配置运行给定的 Operator，并进入回测、优化或实盘等不同工作模式。"
msgstr ""
"Run the given Operator according to the current configuration and enter "
"different working modes such as backtesting, optimization, or live trading."

#: of qteasy.core.run:3
msgid ""
"本函数是 qteasy 的统一入口：根据全局配置 ``QT_CONFIG['mode']``（可通过 "
"``qt.configure(mode=...)`` 暂时覆盖），选择实盘模式、回测模式、优化模式等， 自动准备所需数据源与日志对象并调用 "
"``Operator.run()`` 执行完整流程。各模式 的详细行为与输出结构见文档「运行 qteasy 与工作模式」相关章节。"
msgstr ""
"This function is qteasy’s unified entry point: based on the global "
"configuration ``QT_CONFIG['mode']`` (which can be temporarily overridden via"
" ``qt.configure(mode=...)``), it selects live trading mode, backtest mode, "
"optimization mode, etc., automatically prepares the required data sources "
"and log objects, and calls ``Operator.run()`` to execute the full workflow. "
"For detailed behavior and output structure of each mode, see the relevant "
"sections in the documentation “Running qteasy and Working Modes”."

#: of qteasy.core.info qteasy.core.run
msgid "参数"
msgstr "Parameters"

#: of qteasy.core.run:8
msgid "已配置好策略与运行参数的 Operator 对象。"
msgstr ""
"An Operator object with strategies and runtime parameters already "
"configured."

#: of qteasy.core.run:10
msgid ""
"本次运行临时覆盖的配置项，键名需为合法的 qteasy 配置键，例如 "
"``mode``、``asset_pool``、``invest_start``、``invest_end`` 等。"
msgstr ""
"Configuration items temporarily overridden for this run; the key names must "
"be valid qteasy configuration keys, such as ``mode``, ``asset_pool``, "
"``invest_start``, ``invest_end``, etc."

#: of qteasy.core.info qteasy.core.run
msgid "返回"
msgstr "Returns"

#: of qteasy.core.run:13
msgid ""
"当 ``mode == 1``（回测模式）时通常返回包含回测结果的字典； 当 ``mode == 2``（优化模式）时通常返回包含多组参数结果的列表； "
"实盘模式与其他模式的具体返回结构详见 Operator.run() 与相关文档说明。"
msgstr ""
"When ``mode == 1`` (backtest mode), it usually returns a dict containing "
"backtest results; when ``mode == 2`` (optimization mode), it usually returns"
" a list containing results for multiple parameter sets; for the exact return"
" structure in live trading mode and other modes, see Operator.run() and the "
"related documentation."

#: of qteasy.core.info qteasy.core.run
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr "Return type"

#: of qteasy.core.info:11 qteasy.core.run:19
msgid "示例"
msgstr "Example"

